{"books":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":[""],"article":{"title":"我们主张（诗）","authors":["四川","李一痕"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":6}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"text":"我们主张（诗）","type":"title"},{"text":"四川李一痕","type":"authors"},{"text":"我们主张   　丁(省公安厅干部李一痕)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"……","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我们主张，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"大张旗鼓地","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"深入群众，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"深入实际，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"发动全局，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"由下而上，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"由党内到党外，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"把，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"一切“丑恶”公开出来！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"让：","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"每张“百扇窗”打开来！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"使：","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"光明普照大地，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"叫：","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“鬼哭”神嚎！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"但愿","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"从此后","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"普天同庆。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"火——整风颂    　　小丁(即李一痕)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"火终于烧起来了，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"越烧越猛…………’","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我添进一颗炭，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"又扬起一阵风，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"大家都来添炭，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"人们一起扬风，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"火光飞舞，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"闪星晶莹，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"让：","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"一场大火燎过原野烧尽人间一切莠花，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"毒草，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"但愿今后：","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"鲜花满园，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"绿草长青，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"春意融融。","type":"paragraph"}],"comments":[],"origin":"《四川省右派言论选辑4》(内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印)，中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年7月28日。","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":0,"page_end":0,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}